{"word":"ποτίζω","slug":"ποτίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ποτίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πότος\">πότος</a></el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πίνω\">πίνω</a></el>] ‘furnish liquid for drinking’, most <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to water<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b>give to drink <a href='B:470 10:42'>Mt 10:42</a>; <a href='B:470 25:35'>25:35</a>, <a href='B:470 25:37'>37</a>; <a href='B:470 27:48'>27:48</a>; <a href='B:520 12:20'>Ro 12:20</a>;</b> in imagery <b><a href='B:530 3:2'>1 Cor 3:2</a>; <a href='B:530 12:13'>12:13</a>; <a href='B:730 14:8'>Rv 14:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of animals <b><a href='B:490 13:15'>Lk 13:15</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> of plants, in imagery <b><a href='B:530 3:6-8'>1 Cor 3:6-8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ποτήριον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Ποτίολοι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}